    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help but it doesn't change what's happening to my body. therapy and meds just feel like putting a bandaid on a severed limb. it's not even about being 'sad' anymore, it's just that the physical reality of living is so unbearable. i keep thinking about how peaceful it would be if everything just finally went still. like, if the noise and the burning just stopped forever. does that sound crazy?",
